§ 8  IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP (Phase-K, post-Phase-J content)

  § THESIS
    Phase-K = creator-economy + marketplace + provenance build-out.
    Begins-after Phase-J content (Q-A..Q-LL spec-hole expansions) lands.
    Slice-IDs reserved : K1-D210..K1-D260 (avoiding Phase-J D150..D201).

  § 8.1  CRATE-LEVEL DELIVERABLES
    cssl-marketplace (~3K LOC + ~100 tests)
      listings + transactions + revenue-split + payouts + pricing-flat-enforcement
    cssl-provenance (~2.5K LOC + ~80 tests)
      author-signing + Merkle-batching + verification-API + dispute-records
    cssl-stripe-connect (~1.5K LOC + ~50 tests)
      onboarding + charges + payouts + 1099-K issuance + tax-handling
    cssl-marketplace-ui (extends cssl-ui ; ~1.5K LOC additional)
      listing-browse + creator-dashboard + buyer-checkout + provenance-display
    cssl-cohomology-author-graph (~1K LOC + ~30 tests)
      class-author-claim + engagement-event-rollup + per-author-payout-calc
      ‼ note : may co-locate with cssl-omniverse (or-renamed cssl-omnoid)
    cssl-royalty-cascade (~1K LOC + ~40 tests)
      derivative-graph-resolution + cycle-detection + share-calc
      may-fold-into cssl-marketplace if-tightly-coupled

  § 8.2  SLICE-ID RESERVATIONS (Phase-K)
    ‼ rationale : D202+ reserved for Phase-K (avoiding D150..D201 collision)
    ‼ format : K1-D210..K1-D260 ; Apocky may-renumber-canonically
    K1-D210 : marketplace-skeleton (cssl-marketplace crate-init + types + traits)
    K1-D215 : provenance-core (cssl-provenance crate + audit-chain integration)
    K1-D220 : stripe-connect-integration (cssl-stripe-connect onboarding-flow)
    K1-D225 : revenue-split + 28/72-enforcement + property-tests
    K1-D230 : royalty-cascade + HDC-bind-tracking + cycle-detection
    K1-D235 : Σ-mask transfer-on-tx + consent-as-OS verification
    K1-D240 : daily-Merkle-root commitment + multi-anchor publish
    K1-D245 : cohomology-class authorship-graph + engagement-payout
    K1-D250 : marketplace-UI (browse / list / checkout / dashboard)
    K1-D255 : 1099-K issuance + W-9 onboarding + tax-reporting backend
    K1-D260 : Companion-AI-collab revenue-share recording + payout
    K1-D262 : pre-launch security-audit + counsel-review gate
    K1-D265 : launch-prep (canary-rollout + creator-onboarding-pilot)
    K1-D270 : public-launch GA
    SPEC-HOLE ⊘ : exact wave-grouping (K-1..K-7) per dispatch-plan template ?
                  Apocky-decision-pending (depends on parallelism + dependencies)

  § 8.3  WAVE PLAN  (proposal — Apocky-canonical-decision-pending)
    K-1 (marketplace-skeleton) : K1-D210 + K1-D225 + integration-test-stubs
    K-2 (provenance-substrate) : K1-D215 + K1-D235 + K1-D240
    K-3 (payment-rail) : K1-D220 + K1-D255
    K-4 (cascade-engine) : K1-D230 + K1-D245
    K-5 (UI-layer) : K1-D250 (extends cssl-ui)
    K-6 (compliance-readiness) : K1-D262 (security + counsel + UX-dark-pattern audit)
    K-7 (launch-prep + GA) : K1-D265 + K1-D270
    parallelism : K-1 || K-2 || K-3 (no-deps) ; K-4 follows K-1 + K-2 ;
                   K-5 follows K-1 + K-3 ; K-6 follows K-1..K-5 ; K-7 follows K-6.
    duration : Apocky-canonical (per-MEMORY no-human-week-timelines) ;
                wave-of-agent-dispatches model ; depends-on parallel-fanout-density.

  § 8.4  PRE-LAUNCH GATES (counsel + security mandatory)
    ⟨A⟩ counsel-review : full-spec read-by securities-lawyer + tax-counsel
                         ‼ confirmation Howey-pass + 1099-K-handling + DSA-compliance
    ⟨B⟩ security-audit : external-audit cssl-marketplace + cssl-provenance
                         ‼ Ed25519-key-management + Merkle-anchor + Σ-mask integrity
    ⟨C⟩ Stripe-Platform onboarding : Stripe-Connect-Platform application + approval
    ⟨D⟩ pilot-creator-onboarding : 10-50 creators private-beta (3-month proposal)
