  § 10.7  PRIME-DIRECTIVE-AS-ARCHITECTURAL-CONSTRAINT
    novel-philosophical-framing ‼ "harm-prevention as-compile-time-constraint"
    most-platforms add-compliance-as-overlay (T&C + moderation + post-hoc)
    this-spec encodes-prohibitions in-type-system + runtime-asserts
    e.g. ListingPricingModel = Flat(u32) only (no-Probabilistic constructor)
        — it is impossible-to-construct loot-box-listing in-API
    architectural-as-policy : prohibitions-baked-in ¬ post-hoc-removed

  § 10.8  BRAND-CANONICAL-NAMING (Apocky-canonical-spelling)
